{"tid":137600,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(有片) 何文田某Dog Cafe虐待狗隻!!!","createTime":"2017-02-28T02:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T01:34:25.000Z","uid":84759,"like":121,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"06863c52383db877c5842b9040ddd04aea2f6604","tid":137600,"uid":84759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:44:52.000Z","msg":"今日睇到一個外國Youtuber黎左香港既Vlog，佢地去左個Dog Cafe之後發現個個Dog Cafe虐待入面既狗。<br />\n<br />\n首先間Cafe會每人收$150蚊既入場費，雖然送小食，但收$150已經好唔合理<br />\n<br />\n之後個Youtuber仲講左好多個老細會無緣無故用shock collar電D狗同打狗既嘢，之後仲有片見到佢地會踢D狗 (10:12秒開始)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eMDEI9O1z04&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=10m12s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeMDEI9O1z04%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D10m12s&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=36286fea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eMDEI9O1z04&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=10m12s</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pq1uSy2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpq1uSy2.jpg&h=11813a83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我已經打左去SPCA搵人跟，但驚無人理<br />\n希望大家幫手諗下辦法救D動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n間Cafe既Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/On-Dog-Dog-Caf%C3%A9/325336184220746\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpages%2FOn-Dog-Dog-Caf%25C3%25A9%2F325336184220746&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a84fea35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pages/On-Dog-Dog-Caf%C3%A9/325336184220746</a>"},{"pid":"04406cec3d50a38ee2e9dfc38f8a164dff3c5a8d","tid":137600,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8c4d0be06a9c6