\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10fa1cafc6dd67cd90fb856f55a86de5d2318f2d","tid":137600,"uid":73947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:28:04.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 個老闆真係好撚on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說我隻狗4個月大個陣開始有行為問題，之後係自己搞唔掂既情況下上網搵trainer 搵到佢地 。<br />\n帶左狗狗上去比佢睇下個情況，佢就話放低比佢搞。 <br />\n放左一星期。返到屋企個問題仲嚴重左，後來搵第二個先知原來佢根本唔識教。 (個個星期一係搵佢啲狗嚇我隻狗 ，一係就鬧，拍打個籠。 )我後尾返到屋企再問佢情況無改善應該點做。佢第一句答我比多600佢上多堂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我真係多謝佢。我相信唔止我一個中伏"},{"pid":"9bd168856e2befac6055081205086f1598c75885","tid":137600,"uid":7453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"見過佢train狗 戇鳩到一個極點<br />\n睇埋條片先知佢有踢狗既習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eadd06139ea8f29d9f2329f9f79630cd8575590","tid":137600,"uid":67656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:39:25.000Z","msg":"幫推！"},{"pid":"f101e8b0799d677a4553950ddde7313d1fc05165","tid":137600,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb5be693ad12d864f616b55c19723f0b23d8c37","tid":137600,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:47:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccbeeeff89a44e2715d6cc7ee26b3f1a32a